# Game Oan Tu Ti (Rock Paper Scissors) - C# WinForms

## 🎮 Gioi thieu
Day la tro choi Oan Tu Ti (Rock Paper Scissors) duoc phat trien bang C# WinForms voi day du cac tinh nang:

### 🌟 Tinh nang chinh:
- **Dang nhap**: He thong dang nhap voi ten nguoi choi
- **Choi don**: Choi voi may tinh (AI ngau nhien)
- **Choi doi**: Choi online voi nguoi khac qua TCP/IP
- **Gioi thieu game**: Huong dan cach choi va luat game
- **Network Monitor**: Cong cu monitor network traffic tuong tu Wireshark

## 🚀 Cach chay ung dung

### Yeu cau he thong:
- .NET 9 SDK
- Windows OS
- Visual Studio 2022 hoac VS Code
- **Admin privileges** (cho Network Monitor)

### Chay ung dung:
1. Mo Terminal/Command Prompt **as Administrator**
2. Navigate den thu muc du an
3. Chay lenh: `dotnet run`

## 📖 Huong dan su dung

### 1. Dang nhap
- Khi khoi dong app, form dang nhap se xuat hien
- Nhap ten nguoi choi
- Click "DANG NHAP" hoac nhan Enter

### 2. Menu chinh
Sau khi dang nhap thanh cong, ban co 4 lua chon:

#### 🎯 Choi don (Single Player)
- Choi voi may tinh
- May se chon ngau nhien
- Diem so duoc tinh tu dong
- Co nut Reset de choi lai
- **Icons**: Hình bàn tay thay vì búa-kéo-bao truyền thống

#### 🌐 Choi doi (Multi Player)
- **Tao phong**: Click "TAO PHONG" de lam host
- **Tham gia phong**: Nhap Room ID va click "VAO PHONG"
- Can 2 nguoi choi de bat dau
- Game se tu dong so sanh ket qua
- **Icons**: Hình bàn tay sinh động

#### 📚 Gioi thieu game
- Xem luat choi va cach thuc hoat dong
- Huong dan chi tiet ve game

#### 🔍 Network Monitor
- **Chuc nang tuong tu Wireshark**
- Capture va phan tich network traffic real-time
- Hien thi packets TCP, UDP, ICMP
- Filter packets theo protocol
- Export du lieu ra CSV/TXT
- Hien thi chi tiet packet (hex dump)
- Thong ke real-time theo protocol

## 🔗 Cau truc ma nguon

### Cac file chinh:
- `Form1.cs` - Form menu chinh
- `LoginForm.cs` - Form dang nhap
- `SinglePlayerForm.cs` - Form choi don
- `MultiPlayerForm.cs` - Form choi doi (TCP networking)
- `GameIntroForm.cs` - Form gioi thieu
- `NetworkMonitorForm.cs` - Form network monitoring
- `NetworkCapture.cs` - Engine capture packets
- `GameConfig.cs` - Cac cau hinh game
- `NetworkUtils.cs` - Tien ich network

### Cong nghe su dung:
- **Frontend**: Windows Forms
- **Networking**: TCP/IP Socket
- **Threading**: Multi-threading cho server/client
- **Random**: Algorithm ngau nhien cho AI
- **Packet Capture**: SharpPcap + PacketDotNet
- **Network Analysis**: Raw socket programming

## 🌐 Che do Multiplayer

### Cach hoat dong:
1. **Host** tao phong → Server TCP lang nghe port 7777
2. **Client** tham gia → Ket noi den localhost:7777
3. Trao doi du lieu qua TCP stream
4. Dong bo lua chon va tinh diem

### Giao thuc tin nhan:
- `PLAYER:[ten]` - Gui ten nguoi choi
- `CHOICE:[lua chon]` - Gui lua chon (Da/Giay/Keo)
- `RESULT:[ket qua]` - Ket qua tran dau

## 🔍 Network Monitor

### Tinh nang Wireshark:
- **Real-time packet capture** tren tat ca network interfaces
- **Protocol detection**: TCP, UDP, ICMP, Ethernet
- **Packet filtering** voi Berkeley Packet Filter syntax
- **Packet details**: Source/Destination IP, Ports, Protocol info
- **Hex dump viewer** cho raw packet data
- **Statistics dashboard** hien thi so luong packets theo protocol
- **Export capabilities** ra CSV hoac text files
- **Auto-scroll** va manual navigation
- **Interface selection** cho multi-NIC systems

### Su dung Network Monitor:
1. Chon network interface tu dropdown
2. (Tuy chon) Nhap filter expression (vd: "tcp port 80", "udp", "icmp")
3. Click "BAT DAU CAPTURE" de bat dau
4. Xem packets real-time trong bang
5. Click vao packet de xem chi tiet
6. Su dung "XUAT FILE" de luu du lieu
7. Click "DUNG CAPTURE" de ket thuc

### Filter Examples:
- `tcp` - Chi hien thi TCP packets
- `udp port 53` - Chi DNS queries
- `icmp` - Chi ping packets
- `host 192.168.1.1` - Chi traffic den/tu IP nay
- `port 80 or port 443` - Chi HTTP/HTTPS traffic

## 🎨 Giao dien

### Mau sac:
- **Da**: Xam nhat (Rock - Gray) với icon ✊
- **Giay**: Xanh nhat (Paper - Light Blue) với icon 🖐️
- **Keo**: Vang nhat (Scissors - Light Yellow) với icon ✌️

### Bieu tuong moi:
- ✊ **Nắm đấm** (Rock) - thay cho icon búa cũ
- 🖐️ **Bàn tay mở** (Paper) - thay cho icon giấy cũ  
- ✌️ **Hai ngón tay** (Scissors) - thay cho icon kéo cũ

## ⚠️ Xu ly loi

### Cac loi thuong gap:
1. **Loi ket noi**: Kiem tra firewall va port 7777
2. **Mat ket noi**: Tu dong hien thi thong bao loi
3. **Thread exception**: Su dung Invoke de update UI thread-safe
4. **Network Monitor loi**: Can quyen Administrator de capture packets
5. **SharpPcap loi**: Kiem tra WinPcap/Npcap da cai dat

### Khac phuc Network Monitor:
- **Chay as Administrator** de co quyen capture packets
- Cai dat **Npcap** neu chua co: https://npcap.com/
- Kiem tra Windows Firewall settings
- Thu chon interface khac neu current interface khong hoat dong

